{"comments":"Allocation.Strategy — Frame allocation algorithms.\n\n## Purpose\n\nImplements allocation strategies for distributing rendering resources:\n- Basic adaptive allocation (P0)\n- FAA-enhanced submodular optimization (P2)\n\n## Architecture\n\n```\nViewportState + PerformanceState + AllocationState\n                     ↓\n          allocateFrame / allocateFrameFAA\n                     ↓\n             AllocationResult\n```\n\n## Algorithm Selection\n\n- allocateFrame: Simple tier-based allocation for real-time use\n- allocateFrameFAA: Optimal allocation via submodular optimization\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Allocate rendering resources for a frame.\n\nAdapts allocation based on performance feedback:\n- If quality headroom is high (>0.7): use tier defaults\n- If quality headroom is medium (0.3-0.7): reduce background quality\n- If quality headroom is low (<0.3): reduce peripheral and background\n\nWill be enhanced with full submodular optimization in P2.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","FrameState","Viewport"],"ViewportState"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","FrameState","Performance"],"PerformanceState"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","FrameState","Allocation","Types"],"AllocationState"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","FrameState","Allocation","Types"],"AllocationResult"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[158,90],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/FrameState/Allocation/Strategy.purs","start":[158,1]},"title":"allocateFrame"},{"children":[],"comments":"Adaptive selection: adjust diffusion steps based on quality headroom.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Core"],"Region"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Core"],"RegionSelection"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[190,57],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/FrameState/Allocation/Strategy.purs","start":[190,1]},"title":"adaptiveSelection"},{"children":[],"comments":"Adjust diffusion steps based on quality headroom and tier.\n\n- Foveal: always gets full steps (highest priority)\n- Peripheral: reduced when quality < 0.5\n- Background: reduced when quality < 0.7\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Core"],"RenderTier"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Core"],"DiffusionSteps"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Core"],"DiffusionSteps"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[203,82],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/FrameState/Allocation/Strategy.purs","start":[203,1]},"title":"adjustStepsForQuality"},{"children":[],"comments":"Allocate frame using FAA-enhanced submodular optimization.\n\n## Algorithm\n\n1. Convert regions to ground set\n2. Create utility oracle (quality + coverage)\n3. Create cardinality matroid (k = maxRegions)\n4. Run FAA-enhanced continuous greedy (√T iterations)\n5. Round using min-energy selection (deterministic)\n6. Convert selected elements back to RegionSelections\n\n## Guarantees (Proven in proofs/Hydrogen/Optimize/Submodular/)\n\n- (1 - 1/e - O(1/√T)) approximation to optimal k-region selection\n- √T iterations instead of T (FAA speedup)\n- Deterministic rounding (min-energy)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","FrameState","Viewport"],"ViewportState"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","FrameState","Performance"],"PerformanceState"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","FrameState","Allocation","Types"],"AllocationState"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","FrameState","Allocation","Types"],"FAAAllocationConfig"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","FrameState","Allocation","Types"],"AllocationResult"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[327,22],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/FrameState/Allocation/Strategy.purs","start":[322,1]},"title":"allocateFrameFAA"},{"children":[],"comments":"Adaptive selection for FAA: use fractional value to modulate steps.\n\nRegions with higher fractional values in the continuous solution\nget more diffusion steps, as they were \"more selected\" by the optimizer.\n\n## Fractional Value Modulation\n\nThe continuous greedy produces fractional values x_e ∈ [0, 1] for each\nelement. After rounding, we use these values to modulate quality:\n- x_e close to 1.0: strong selection → more diffusion steps\n- x_e close to 0.5: marginal selection → baseline diffusion steps\n- x_e close to 0.0: weak selection (shouldn't happen after rounding)\n\nThe fractional value acts as a \"confidence\" weight from the optimizer.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Optimize","Submodular","Continuous","FractionalSolution"],"FractionalSolution"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","FrameState","Allocation","Types"],"RegionIndex"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","FrameState","Allocation","Types"],"Tuple"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Core"],"Region"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Core"],"RegionSelection"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[401,21],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/FrameState/Allocation/Strategy.purs","start":[397,1]},"title":"adaptiveSelectionFAA"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert regions to a ground set for submodular optimization.\n\nEach region becomes an Element indexed by position in the array.\nReturns (groundSet, indexToRegion) for mapping back after optimization.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Array"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Core"],"Region"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["groundSet",{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Optimize","Submodular","Types","GroundSet"],"GroundSet"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","FrameState","Allocation","Types"],"RegionIndex"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["indexToRegion",{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Array"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Core"],"Region"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[225,111],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/FrameState/Allocation/Strategy.purs","start":[225,1]},"title":"regionsToGroundSetFAA"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create a submodular oracle for region allocation.\n\n## Utility Function\n\nThe utility of selecting a set of regions S is:\n\n  f(S) = qualityWeight · Σ_{r ∈ S} tierQuality(r)\n       + coverageWeight · coverage(S)\n\nWhere:\n- tierQuality(r) = 1.0 for Foveal, 0.6 for Peripheral, 0.3 for Background\n- coverage(S) = √|S| (concave, encouraging spread)\n\n## Submodularity\n\nThe function is submodular because:\n- Linear sum is modular (trivially submodular)\n- √|S| is concave in |S| (submodular)\n- Non-negative sum of submodular functions is submodular\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","FrameState","Allocation","Types"],"FAAAllocationConfig"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Array"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Render","Online","Core"],"Region"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Optimize","Submodular","Types","GroundSet"],"GroundSet"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","FrameState","Allocation","Types"],"RegionIndex"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Optimize","Submodular","Types","Function"],"SubmodularOracle"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","GPU","FrameState","Allocation","Types"],"RegionIndex"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[255,34],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/FrameState/Allocation/Strategy.purs","start":[251,1]},"title":"regionUtilityOracle"},{"children":[],"comments":"Safe Int to Number conversion without FFI.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[416,30],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/FrameState/Allocation/Strategy.purs","start":[416,1]},"title":"intToNumSafe"}],"name":"Hydrogen.GPU.FrameState.Allocation.Strategy","reExports":[]}